.SH "NAME"
equo \- Official Sabayon Linux Package Manager Client
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
\&\fBequo\fR [action] [basic_options] [options|extended_options] [atom | package_file | \f(CW@set\fR] ...
.PP
